# Vercel AI SDK Skill

- Use the Vercel AI SDK (`ai` and `@ai-sdk/google`) for all LLM generations.
- Specifically, use the Google provider and the latest Flash model by calling: `google('gemini-3-flash-preview')`.
- To generate the "Experiment Plan" (Protocol, Materials, Budget, Timeline), use the `streamObject` function from the AI SDK.
- Always define a strict Zod schema (`z.object({...})`) for the Experiment Plan to ensure the LLM outputs exact fields for the budget (with £/$), timeline, and step-by-step protocol.
- Do not use the legacy `OpenAIStream`. Use the App Router native `streamObject` or `streamText` methods.